      "html": "<h3>Task 6: Complete the conversation. For questions 1-6 mark the correct letter A-H. (6 points)</h3>"
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "html": "<p><b>Professor and student talking</b></p><p><b>Student:</b> Excuse me, professor. Would it be possible to arrange a meeting with you sometime this week? I need your advice concerning my project.</p><p><b>Professor:</b> <b>(1)</b></p><p><b>Student:</b> Do you mean the one on the second floor of the main university building?</p><p><b>Professor:</b> <b>(2)</b></p><p><b>Student:</b> I&rsquo;ll definitely keep you informed, professor, but I hope this won&rsquo;t happen.</p><p><b>Professor:</b> <b>(3)</b></p><p><b>Student:</b> I had some personal problems that led to missing two of your lectures and that&rsquo;s the reason.</p><p><b>Professor:</b> <b>(4)</b></p><p><b>Student:</b> I did go through them but I would still appreciate some clarification.</p><p><b>Professor:</b> <b>(5)</b></p><p><b>Student:</b> Thank you. I&rsquo;ll do that. But does this mean that I won&rsquo;t be able to submit my project this week?</p><p><b>Professor:</b> <b>(6)</b></p><p><b>Student:</b> Excellent! Thank you so much, professor. I&rsquo;ll do my best to meet the new deadline.</p>"
    },
    {
      "kind": "wordbank",
      "mode": "sentences",
      "words": [
        {
          "letter": "A",
          "text": "It&rsquo;s a pity you couldn&rsquo;t meet the project deadline on time."
        },
        {
          "letter": "B",
          "text": "Well, in that case, I&rsquo;ll be giving the same lecture for group B on Wednesday. Why don&rsquo;t you attend it?"
        },
        {
          "letter": "C",
          "text": "Let me check my schedule. How about this Friday at 3 pm? Can we meet in the physics lab?"
        },
        {
          "letter": "D",
          "text": "Sure, we can meet any time. I have some free time this Friday noon."
        },
        {
          "letter": "E",
          "text": "The deadline for submitting late projects is at the end of next week, so don&rsquo;t worry about that."
        },
        {
          "letter": "F",
          "text": "I understand. Can you check with other students about the online resources I recommended for the project?"
        },
        {
          "letter": "G",
          "text": "Really? What is it that you couldn&rsquo;t quite understand - the theory or something else?"
        },
        {
          "letter": "H",
          "text": "Exactly. Please don&rsquo;t forget to give me a call if you need to reschedule the meeting."
        }
      ]
    },
